{
  "stem": "1929.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 427.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And talked to them, the woman, and then she finally told him not to, that they didn't steal it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother did-- was trying to make contact during that time and before with the underground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they, according to him, they were-- they had no interest in any Jews joining the partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had no interest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The only one that had any kind of a lukewarm interest were the communists of the different partisan political groups.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the main one, the Christian ones, did not want the Jews at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Russians are-- the Russians are very close to where we-- where we were at.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I knew it from the attitude of the Ukrainians and the soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were fearful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very fearful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were getting drunk and drunker every day because they knew that their punishment was going to be more severe than anybody's because they were really Russians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians were not Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were deal-- dealt with them the same ways the Germans would, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I don't remember-- this is-- this is the thing that I've been struggling with, is that I know from talking to my cousin and others who have survived the camp with me, that in 19-- November of 1944, which is the end of 1944, that the camp was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I have no memory of that whatsoever, except I remember the cattle cars waiting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where my memory wakes up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until then, I don't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember-- I was questioning my cousin, how did we get?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did we walk?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How far was it from there to the railroad yard?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
